4x4 - low quality
8x8 - best mix
16x16 - highest

linear - non pbr
srgb - pbr

ANM/NM/MISC/RM/MASK/CM

RED-RED-RED-GREEN
r - g - b - a

BC - convert in paint.net to TGA then in PVRTexTool to astc srgb

Don't use Nvidia Tool for TexTool step - worse quality

If you can't open BC in any program then convert it to tga in Nvidia Texture Tool


HD textures - single resolution
Usual textures - two times smaller res + full mip mapping 
